AI-GENERATION DISCLOSURE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
These images are AI-generated. Each panel was baked by OpenAI's image
generation tool (invoked via the `codex` CLI) from a deterministic SVG content
blueprint plus a fixed character identity reference, then accepted by a
cross-model review gate. No panel is a photograph or a hand-drawn work, and no
copyrighted third-party artwork was used as a reference or training condition by
this project.

Outputs of generative image models may carry usage terms from the model
provider, and the copyright status of purely AI-generated images varies by
jurisdiction. The CC-BY-4.0 grant above is offered to the extent the author
holds rights in these specific generated artifacts; it does not override the
